Required perl modules:
------------------------------------

see ../bin/bbbike-build-runtime-perl.pl

Required debian modules
------------------------------------

pbzip2 git-core openjdk-6-jdk screen lynx curl wget 
pigz make libhtml-tagcloud-perl buffer pktstat libtext-unidecode-perl perltidy
libxml-atom-simplefeed-perl libjson-perl liburi-perl libxml-libxml-perl libyaml-perl libyaml-syck-perl tidy


Development
------------------------------------

# download planet.osm, extract and convert city data
$ time make update-database

# extract data for a city and build a bbbike database
$ time make CITIES="Augsburg Halle" cities convert

# extract and convert only
$ time make bbbike_cleanup="" update-database

# check a city area
$ ./world/bin/bbbike-db --city-stat | grep Bielefeld
Bielefeld =>    69.3    Bielefeld:de,en,da,es,fr,hr,nl,pl,pt,ru,zh 

